node.text:
📣 Giveaway Alert! 📣 Rave about your fave! Which one of our exclusive @CotonColors Flavor Mugs is your favorite? Tell us in the comments for your chance to win. We’ll randomly select five lucky guests to receive a $50 Nothing Bundt Cakes gift card!
-
Availability may vary by bakery.
-
*For official rules, please visit the link in our bio. One entry per person. We’ll direct message the winners to redeem their prize! No Purch. Nec. 8/20, 12:01am CT thru 8/20, 11:59pm CT. 18+. U.S. and Canada residents. Not sponsored by Instagram. For giveaways, we will never ask for personal data beyond a name and mailing address for us to send the gift card to. For any questions or concerns, please contact Promotions@NothingBundtCakes.com 
-
#NothingBundtCakes #BundtCake #CotonColors #CotonColorsxNothingBundtCake #Giveaway #Contest
